  "content": "════════════════════════ -->\n<div class=\"slide slide-2\">\n  <div class=\"slide-inner\">\n    <div class=\"slide-label\">The Why</div>\n    <div class=\"slide-title\">Why Build <span class=\"hl-blue\">This</span>?</div>\n    <div class=\"motivation-list\">\n      <div class=\"motivation-item\">\n        <span class=\"m-icon\">🧠</span>\n        <div class=\"m-text\">Learn about generative AI firsthand. Not by reading. By building in it and feeling the impact directly.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"motivation-item\">\n        <span class=\"m-icon\">🧰</span>\n        <div class=\"m-text\">Own my development tool. Every role change, I waste time rebuilding my environment. I wanted something portable.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"motivation-item\">\n        <span class=\"m-icon\">📂</span>\n        <div class=\"m-text\">Build a portfolio that ships. Not a tutorial project. A real product I'd use every day.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"distinction\">\n      <div class=\"distinction-card\" style=\"border-top: 3px solid var(--text-muted);\">\n        <div class=\"d-label\" style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\">Personal memory</div>\n        <div class=\"d-example\">\"use tabs not spaces in this project\"</div>\n        <div class=\"d-note\" style=\"color: var(--text-muted);\">CLAUDE.md, Cursor rules, Copilot</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"distinction-card\" style=\"border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-cyan);\">\n        <div class=\"d-label\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">Organizational memory</div>\n        <div class=\"d-example\">\"auth was redesigned across 3 repos last month. Here are the trade-offs and what testing revealed.\"</div>\n        <div class=\"d-note\" style=\"color: var(--accent-cyan);\">corvia</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <span>Lim Chun Zhe</span>\n      <span>2 / 10</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
